<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹的想法是这样的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想到了需要帮助的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想到了孤独和走失的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想到了需要朋友的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想到了孤儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹知道没有家人是什么感觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多陌生人曾对他很友善，而且给了他很多东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他记得蓝色小仙女说过，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从陌生人那里得到帮助是件好事，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是帮助陌生人是件更好的事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去帮助那些没有爸爸妈妈的孩子。”他决定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹终于找到了通往孤儿院的路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个地方很小，院子里有很多枯树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要帮他们移开这些树枝。”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用绳子把树枝捆起来，然后拉走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把院子里所有的树枝都清理干净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看到了他，都从里面跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，一头驴！”他们喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多么棒的驴啊。”一个女孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能骑你吗，驴先生？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹点点头。于是女孩儿爬了上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他带着一个又一个孩子绕着院子走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们开心地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚饭的时候，孩子们跑进屋里吃通心面条。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹很饿，他很想进屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他想变得慷慨一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他吃了些草，睡在了外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天，匹诺曹都在孤儿院工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他让孩子们骑着他去城里买食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把草吃短点，好让孩子们玩得安全。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他搬运柴火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有任何艰难的工作，匹诺曹都很乐意帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下午，他会坐在房子外面听孩子们上课。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们，二加二等于几？”老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“四！”他们都喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们，我们国家的首都是哪个城市？”老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗马！”他们喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。”老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，到了讲故事的时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹喜欢听老师讲故事，所以他听得很认真。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从前有一个名叫约拿的男人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不想听上帝的话，于是逃跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他被一只鲸鱼吞到了肚子里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在鲸鱼的肚子里待了三天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>由于他非常后悔没有听上帝的话，鲸鱼又把他吐了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要听上帝的话，孩子们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“约拿在鲸鱼肚子里活着？那么爸爸也一定在鲸鱼肚子里活着！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蓝色小仙女说过他很安全，还被藏起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一定是在鲸鱼肚子里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噢，如果我待在学校里，我早就能听到这些故事了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我早就可以把爸爸救出来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，匹诺曹发生了巨大的变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的蹄子变成了手指，他的耳朵变小了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的毛脱落了，他的声音听起来又像男孩儿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“成功了！”他喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蓝色小仙女是对的！我既慷慨又勤劳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，我又能做回男孩儿了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹以最快的速度跑向大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次他再也不会停了，不会因为金子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>或者马戏团，或者天堂而停下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他要找到杰佩托！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>